{"tid":1278401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科大校長史維：譴責暴力之餘　應探討事件成因","createTime":"2019-07-02T12:25:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T12:31:58.000Z","uid":51271,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6754ef2166822b510707872c0b9c44e4b4a958ed","tid":1278401,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:25:39.000Z","msg":"科大校長史維向全校發信，指昨天立法會發生的事件令人困擾及傷心，有關暴力行為要被譴責，但不應個別解讀事件，須觀察過去數星期的情況，如何引致昨晚的事情。<br />\n<br />\n史維指，大多數示威者都是年輕人和學生，他們充份了解後果後，仍作出相關行動，大家應探討事情的根本原因。<br />\n<br />\n史維表示，現時最重要是各方直接對話，以開放的態度彼此聆聽，緩和社會的緊張氣氛，重複相同的立場或持續對立，只會令香港更分化，香港會成為終極輸家。任何人關心香港的未來，都應該出力促成對話。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466296-20190702.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466296-20190702.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPkwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=1ea8be3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466296-20190702.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8457e47d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466296-20190702.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"9c7035dbfef2ce3d4a135caeccee597855d5c5dc","tid":1278401,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:29:27.000Z","msg":"8大死剩一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6113986b9d59068f19ee9f7f0f0a2e68bf82abe","tid":1278401,"uid":71253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:30:58.000Z","msg":"段崇智：汪汪汪"},{"pid":"82b0f9e2e7a3c7fe3cf36a14fcaa159f632021ba","tid":1278401,"uid":164730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:31:58.000Z","msg":"史維, 台灣裔美國人"}]}